# Private scratch / internal docs — AI reviews, logs, drafts, design notes, the scrapped
# landing-page shell. Internal-only. DO NOT move these to .git/info/exclude — that is
# LOCAL-ONLY and does not travel, so on a fresh clone `git add -A` would sweep them in.
